"NOWPayments allows you to accept credit card payments directly to your "
"crypto wallet. Funds go straight to your wallet – no middleman."
msgstr ""
"NOWPayments inakuwezesha kupokea malipo ya kadi ya mkopo moja kwa moja "
"kwenye pochi yako ya kripti. Fedha zinakuja moja kwa moja kwenye pochi yako "
"– hakuna mfanyakazi wa kati."

