msgid ""
"Stripe Crypto payments (USDC) are ONLY available for US-based businesses. If"
" you are outside the US, Stripe will only accept credit card payments to "
"your Stripe balance (not directly to crypto)."
msgstr ""
"Malipo ya Stripe Crypto (USDC) ziko TU kwa biashara zinazotokana na "
"Marekani. Ukipo nje ya Marekani, Stripe itakubali malipo ya kadi ya mkopo tu"
" kwa salio lako la Stripe (si moja kwa moja kwa kripto)."

msgid ""
"If you are in the US, you can use Stripe to receive crypto directly. If "
"outside, consider NOWPayments or CoinGate for direct crypto payouts."
msgstr ""
"Ukipo Marekani, unaweza kutumia Stripe kupokea kripto moja kwa moja. Ikipo "
"nje, fikiria NOWPayments au CoinGate kwa malipo ya kripto moja kwa moja."

